      "layout": "The page uses a full-bleed, dark layout without a fixed max-width, allowing background elements to extend edge-to-edge. The hero section features a centered headline and description over a dark, atmospheric visual. Content sections maintain consistent vertical spacing of 100px, although specific internal content structures are minimal, mainly focusing on centered text blocks and a single mobile device visual. Navigation is handled by a minimal top-left logo and a hamburger menu icon on the top right, with no visible sticky header.",
